        public ScoredTagging(List<E> tokens,
                     List<String> tags,

        Construct a scored tagging with the specified tokens, tags, and score. The token and tag lists are copied so that subsequent changes to the list will not affect the constructed tagging.
        Parameters:
        tokens - Tokens for the tagging.
        tags - Tags for the tagging.
        score - Score for the tagging.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If the lists are not of the same size.
